      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty quantified; alternative turbulence and hemolysis constitutive models compared; Bayesian model selection applied.",
      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis power-law model used; no model-form uncertainty quantification performed; critical gap at MRL 5."
