      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain model inputs characterized with PDFs; global sensitivity analysis identifies dominant inputs; UQ propagated to QoI.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on flow rate and rotational speed only; blood rheology parameters, hemolysis model constants, and wall compliance not included in UQ sweep."
