      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sample size sufficient for statistical characterization; inter-laboratory reproducibility demonstrated.",
      "rationale": "Single laboratory experimental dataset used; no inter-laboratory comparison available; sample size insufficient for statistical characterization at MRL 5."
