    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps and achieved levels below required levels across all 13 factors, the assessment is formally accepted under the Minimal profile pending supplemental evidence. Six factors remain not-assessed as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Acceptance is conditional and does not imply fitness for regulatory submission without further V&V activities.",
